metadata.name: Funky Liger #1
metadata.description: A start to a new collection of drawings. That I have created. I will be adding new items and also new animals and collections in the future. This is only the beginning. I must note that some of the revenue from this collection will be donated to charitable causes in particularly helping countries that don't have it the best as us and towards helping Cancer research as I have many people I know who have been affected by cancer (not me directly). Meaning it is something close to heart. I will be posting my donations on Twitter to show how we have all helped these causes. If you want to give suggestions on charities don't hesitate to message me on Twitter (I will only donate to official charities). Let me know what you think of the collection of my Twitter.
